{"tid":2081574,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾國衞：作為中國人要珍惜當前美好的年代","createTime":"2020-06-27T10:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-27T16:43:33.000Z","uid":7542,"like":5,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"867c2ab0100445f7227cc3d2292ed19c7e40f88a","tid":2081574,"uid":7542,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-27T10:24:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">做咩唧你，中國美好年代就嚟完啦咩</span></strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局長曾國衞接受央視專訪時表示，對「港區國安法」立法渴望已久，相關立法必將震懾反中亂港分子。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞稱，聽到人大準備要為國安立法時，第一個反應就是「渴望已久」。他指出，香港過去一年經歷反修例風波，對香港治安、國家安全造成明顯風險，因此他非常渴望訂立國安法。他又表示，設立港區國安法體現國家對香港的關愛。<br />\n<br />\n曾國衞表示，港區國安法落實生效後，港府將積極配合相關工作，並對各界廣泛宣傳。他續稱，作為中國人要珍惜當前美好的年代，為國家、民族多作貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200627/s00001/1593241030302/港區國安法-曾國衞-對國安立法渴望已久-體現國家對港關愛\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200627%2Fs00001%2F1593241030302%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E6%9B%BE%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%9E-%E5%B0%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%B8%B4%E6%9C%9B%E5%B7%B2%E4%B9%85-%E9%AB%94%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%9C%E6%84%9B&d=mwjAj24IHyfJiBWsHz9aFpnDgp1V90hxAqV0yKYrtpw%3D&h=b80638ef\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200627%2Fs00001%2F1593241030302%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95-%E6%9B%BE%E5%9C%8B%E8%A1%9E-%E5%B0%8D%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%B8%B4%E6%9C%9B%E5%B7%B2%E4%B9%85-%E9%AB%94%E7%8F%BE%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E5%B0%8D%E6%B8%AF%E9%97%9C%E6%84%9B&h=96181e8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200627/s00001/1593241030302/港區國安法-曾國衞-對國安立法渴望已久-體現國家對港關愛</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n===<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>如果中共倒台，會係唱緊咩歌呢？</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/